maintext:
HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the Pennsylvania Lottery’s “Pick 5 Evening” game were:
6-4-8-3-8, Wild: 8
(six, four, eight, three, eight; Wild: eight)
